<div class="card-form hidden card-local_k3s space-y-4">
  <div class="space-y-4">
    <p class="font-semibold">Setting up a local K3s or K3d cluster:</p>

    <div>
      <p class="font-medium">Option 1: K3d (Docker-based, recommended for macOS)</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 mt-2 ml-4">
        <li>Install K3d: <code class="cursor-pointer" data-controller="clipboard" data-clipboard-text="brew install k3d">brew install k3d</code></li>
        <li>Create a cluster: <code class="cursor-pointer" data-controller="clipboard" data-clipboard-text="k3d cluster create dev">k3d cluster create dev</code></li>
        <li>Get the kubeconfig: <code class="cursor-pointer" data-controller="clipboard" data-clipboard-text="k3d kubeconfig get dev">k3d kubeconfig get dev</code></li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="font-medium">Option 2: K3s (Native)</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 mt-2 ml-4">
        <li>Install K3s: <code class="cursor-pointer" data-controller="clipboard" data-clipboard-text="curl -sfL https://get.k3s.io | sh -">curl -sfL https://get.k3s.io | sh -</code></li>
        <li>Get the kubeconfig: <code class="cursor-pointer" data-controller="clipboard" data-clipboard-text="sudo cat /etc/rancher/k3s/k3s.yaml">sudo cat /etc/rancher/k3s/k3s.yaml</code></li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <p class="font-semibold">Copy the kubeconfig output and paste it below:</p>
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <%= form.label :kubeconfig_output, "Kubeconfig" %>
    <%= form.text_area :kubeconfig_output, class: "textarea textarea-bordered w-full max-w-lg h-48", placeholder: "Paste your kubeconfig here..." %>
  </div>

  <div>
    <%= form.submit "Create Cluster", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</div>
